type LiquidityPool @entity @regularPolling {
  "Unique identifier for the liquidity pool."

  inputTokens: [Token!]!

  outputToken: Token

  rewardTokens: [RewardToken!]

  fees: [LiquidityPoolFee!]!

  isSingleSided: Boolean!
  "Timestamp when the liquidity pool was created."
  createdTimestamp: BigInt!
  "Block number when the liquidity pool was created."
  createdBlockNumber: BigInt!
  "Total value locked in the pool, measured in USD."
  totalValueLockedUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative revenue from the supply side, measured in USD."
  cumulativeSupplySideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative revenue from the protocol side, measured in USD."
  cumulativeProtocolSideRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative total revenue, measured in USD."
  cumulativeTotalRevenueUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Cumulative trading volume, measured in USD."
  cumulativeVolumeUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Balances of input tokens in the pool."
  inputTokenBalances: [BigInt!]!
  "Weights of input tokens in the pool."
  inputTokenWeights: [BigDecimal!]!
  "Total supply of the output token."
  outputTokenSupply: BigInt
  "Price of the output token, measured in USD."
  outputTokenPriceUSD: BigDecimal
  "Amount of output tokens staked."
  stakedOutputTokenAmount: BigInt
  "Amounts of reward token emissions."
  rewardTokenEmissionsAmount: [BigInt!]
  "Reward token emissions, measured in USD."
  rewardTokenEmissionsUSD: [BigDecimal!]
  "Daily snapshots of the liquidity pool's state."
  dailySnapshots: [LiquidityPoolDailySnapshot!]! @derivedFrom(field: "pool")
  "Hourly snapshots of the liquidity pool's state."
  hourlySnapshots: [LiquidityPoolHourlySnapshot!]! @derivedFrom(field: "pool")
  "List of deposit transactions in the pool."
  deposits: [Deposit!]! @derivedFrom(field: "pool")
  "List of withdrawal transactions from the pool."
  withdraws: [Withdraw!]! @derivedFrom(field: "pool")
  "List of swap transactions in the pool."

  "Cumulative amount of trading fees, measured in USD."

  "Cumulative amount of withdrawal fees, measured in USD."
  _cumulativeWithdrawalFeeAmountUSD: BigDecimal!
  "Identifier for the latest reward program."
  _latestRewardProgramID: BigInt!
}"}
